reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for traveling
reviews.reviewText: I have always packed an extension cord when we travel. There never seems to be enough plug ins in hotel rooms and my husband has a c pap machine. It has enough plugs and usb ports for all of our electronics. It is compact and the cord wraps around itself for easy storage. Would be a great gift for the travelers in your life.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wonderful for travel
reviews.reviewText: I wanted a power strip to take with me when I stay with friends and in hotels, to charge my many devices. This fits the bill beautifully. I really like that the cord wraps around the charging platform, so it doesn't end up stuffed in my bag.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is just what I was looking for!
reviews.reviewText: I take this with me every time I travel now. I love it! The ports are just enough and perfect for my necessary on-the-go devices and the flat plug makes fitting it in narrow spots much easier. I love how the cord wraps around and secures on the body rather than getting tied up with everything else. If only everything else were as thoughtfully designed as this is.There was a small issue with the USB ports not powering in the first device I was sent, but the seller was super quick to send a replacement which worked perfectly.
